00024 void Resonators::wake_calc(const f_vector_t& NewTimeArray) {
00025     /*
00026     * Wake calculation method as a function of time.*
00027     */
00028     fTimeArray = NewTimeArray;
00029     fWake.resize(fTimeArray.size());
00030     std::fill_n(fWake.begin(), fWake.size(), 0);
00031     // util::dump(&fWake[0], 10, "start wake ");
00032 
00033     for (uint i = 0; i < fNResonators; ++i) {
00034         ftype alpha = fOmegaR[i] / (2 * fQ[i]);
00035         ftype omega_bar = std::sqrt(fOmegaR[i] * fOmegaR[i] - alpha * alpha);
00036 
00037         for (uint j = 0; j < fWake.size(); ++j) {
00038             ftype temp = fTimeArray[j];
00039             // util::dump(&temp, 1, "temp ");
00040             int sign = (temp > 0) - (temp < 0);
00041             fWake[j] += (sign + 1) * fRS[i] * alpha * std::exp(-alpha * temp) *
00042                         (std::cos(omega_bar * temp) -
00043                          alpha / omega_bar * std::sin(omega_bar * temp));
00044         }
00045     }
00046 }

00048 void Resonators::imped_calc(const f_vector_t& NewFrequencyArray) {
00049     /*
00050     * Impedance calculation method as a function of frequency.*
00051     */
00052 
00053     fFreqArray = NewFrequencyArray;
00054     fImpedance.resize(fFreqArray.size());
00055     // fImpedance[0] = complex_t(0, 0);
00056     std::fill_n(fImpedance.begin(), fImpedance.size(), complex_t(0, 0));
00057     // std::cout << complex_t(1,0) / complex_t(1,1) << '\n';
00058     for (uint i = 0; i < fNResonators; ++i) {
00059         for (uint j = 1; j < fImpedance.size(); ++j) {
00060             fImpedance[j] +=
00061                 complex_t(fRS[i], 0) /
00062                 complex_t(1, fQ[i] * (fFreqArray[j] / fFrequencyR[i] -
00063                                       fFrequencyR[i] / fFreqArray[j]));
00064         }
00065     }
00066 }

00068 InputTable::InputTable(const f_vector_t& input1, const f_vector_t& input2,
00069                        const f_vector_t input3) {
00070     if (input3.empty()) {
00071 
00072         fTimeArray = input1;
00073         fWakeArray = input2;
00074 
00075     } else {
00076         fFrequencyArrayLoaded = input1;
00077         fReZArrayLoaded = input2;

00079         assert(fReZArrayLoaded.size() == fImZArrayLoaded.size());
00080 
00081         for (uint i = 0; i < fReZArrayLoaded.size(); ++i) {
00082             complex_t z(fReZArrayLoaded[i], fImZArrayLoaded[i]);
00083             fImpedanceLoaded.push_back(z);
00084         }
00085 
00086         if (fFrequencyArrayLoaded[0] != 0) {
00087 
00088             fFrequencyArrayLoaded.insert(fFrequencyArrayLoaded.begin(), 0);
00089             fReZArrayLoaded.insert(fReZArrayLoaded.begin(), 0);
00090             fImZArrayLoaded.insert(fImZArrayLoaded.begin(), 0);
00091         }
00092     }

00102     // Impedance calculation method as a function of frequency.*
